{"tid":429610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝻亞人持棍扑爛中銀櫃員機 PTU極速拉人","createTime":"2017-10-09T05:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T11:21:07.000Z","uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b0530a51ccde2ec6f2e631785ce63419c17469d3","tid":429610,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171009/57308908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171009%2F57308908&d=YCODDMybYN7foeKrmTtIoRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=80e2e800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171009%2F57308908&h=1288bc71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171009/57308908</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171009/large/1507523484_0d2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F1507523484_0d2c.jpg&h=094592ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171009/large/1507525792_0a54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F1507525792_0a54.jpg&h=abe8f3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中午近12時，一名男子手持2呎長黑色木棍，走到旺角鬧市，在山東街48號行人路旁中國銀行櫃員機，手起棍落扑爛櫃員機的出鈔位置，然後拔足逃跑。當時對面報紙檔女檔主，以及泊在該處的一部解款車解款員目睹經過，立即報警。在附近巡邏的機動部隊接報，馬上持盾牌趕到搜捕疑人，迅速在通菜街47號後巷截獲該名逞兇者，將他拘捕帶署，警方正調查其作案動機。"},{"pid":"cd68fc105230a388966f2d8bd2edf37fca9675e8","tid":429610,"uid":78420,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"目的根本就係想入監住。"},{"pid":"5909f94c89054d7985157e4122999651576d4656","tid":429610,"uid":19962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"蠢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係以為咁就會岀錢呀？"},{"pid":"32ca04b705fe250624f8f09cccdc7256a8957254","tid":429610,"uid":78420,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係以為咁就會岀錢呀？</blockquote><br />\n精過大部份港豬呀。"},{"pid":"fccc0ed5565bb22a0ef22757019072cdfa18d396","tid":429610,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"蝻亞人都鐘意睇港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226a0a742fbdfd698001fbcb5b79d44de97b2003","tid":429610,"uid":45428,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"扑完就走又唔係拎錢<br />\n唔通真係走投無路想入監倉避世"},{"pid":"ed519980c510968755fd1a7bcd2cf2753ce693d3","tid":429610,"uid":17611,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"架解款員咁得閒泊係個度目擊事發經過<br />\n<br />\n仲要客貨車黎 咁得閒 係咪係度訓教"},{"pid":"e33fe61a9b6e68fe33eb612fba7a6c5712a450a3","tid":429610,"uid":45428,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>架解款員咁得閒泊係個度目擊事發經過<br />\n<br />\n仲要客貨車黎 咁得閒 係咪係度訓教</blockquote><br />\n比著我打萬零蚊工都唔同佢搏啦<br />\n有刀點算呀"},{"pid":"ffd5e0d40c61235c84e2e5f75c8139f45ebdfcdf","tid":429610,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"我疑似見過佢<br />\n喺旺角<br />\n又係揸住碌棍<br />\n行過d 工程圍欄一棍打爆d 上邊d黃色閃燈<br />\n南亞裔 矮身材<br />\n應該又係想入去醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbd9e2c5424d58ba38881e4136f10f5760c2e18","tid":429610,"uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係以為咁就會岀錢呀？</blockquote><br />\n佢都係打爆個Mon啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇個款就未必係想求錢<br />\n可能係有病想博入冊享用免費醫療"